## 5. Configurar CORS no Render (Produção)

### Após deploy do frontend, adicione no Render:

**Para Vercel:**
```
Key: CORS_ORIGINS
Value: http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173,https://seu-app.vercel.app,https://seu-app-git-main.vercel.app
```

**Para Netlify:**
```
Key: CORS_ORIGINS
Value: http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173,https://seu-app.netlify.app,https://deploy-preview-*--seu-app.netlify.app
```

**Para ambos (mais seguro):**
```
Key: CORS_ORIGINS
Value: http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173,https://seu-app.vercel.app,https://seu-app.netlify.app